                    <dt/>
                    <dd/>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry id="dlentry_t1j_cgk_54b">
                    <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Equation16.gif" id="image_f2g_bdt_yjb"
                        />Insert Equation</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>Opens the <uicontrol>XML Fragment Editor</uicontrol> that allows you to
                      insert and <xref href="../topics/author-editing-mathml.dita">edit MathML
                        notations</xref>.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry id="dlentry_u1j_cgk_54b">
                    <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Paragraph16.png" id="image_g2g_bdt_yjb"
                        />Insert Paragraph</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>Inserts a new <term>paragraph</term> element at current cursor
                      position.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry id="dlentry_v1j_cgk_54b">
                    <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Section16.gif" id="image_h2g_bdt_yjb"/>Insert
                        Section</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>Inserts a new <term>section</term> element in the document, depending on the
                      current context.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-author-actions/insert_xinclude_dlentry" id="dlentry_w1j_cgk_54b">
                    <dt/>
                    <dd/>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry id="dlentry_x1j_cgk_54b">
                    <dt><uicontrol>Insert Entity</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>Allows you to insert a predefined entity or character entity. Surrogate
                      character entities (range #x10000 to #x10FFFF) are also accepted. Character
                      entities can be entered in one of the following forms: <ul id="ul_t3w_twm_ps">
                        <li id="li_y1j_cgk_54b">#<i>&lt;decimal value&gt;</i> - e.g. #65</li>
                        <li id="li_z1j_cgk_54b">&amp;#<i>&lt;decimal value&gt;</i> - e.g. &amp;#65</li>
                        <li id="li_abj_cgk_54b">#x<i>&lt;hexadecimal value&gt;</i> - e.g. #x41</li>
                        <li id="li_bbj_cgk_54b">&amp;#x<i>&lt;hexadecimal value&gt;</i> - e.g. &amp;#x41</li>
                      </ul></dd>
                  </dlentry>
                </dl>
